1
00:00:17,053 --> 00:00:18,488
[grunt]

2
00:00:19,688 --> 00:00:21,290
<i>(Ninja)</i>
<i>It's the enemy!</i>

3
00:00:22,224 --> 00:00:23,392
<i>(Ninja)</i>
<i>Here they come!</i>

4
00:00:30,197 --> 00:00:33,366
{\an1}[grunt] Damn it!
There's just no
end to these guys!

5
00:00:34,066 --> 00:00:37,702
{\an4}All we're doing is
getting worn out.
How long is this
going to last?

6
00:00:38,537 --> 00:00:41,373
{\an1}That's rain...

7
00:00:43,474 --> 00:00:44,841
{\an1}But the sun's out...

8
00:00:44,874 --> 00:00:46,776
<i>(Ninja)</i>
<i>They're coming from</i>
<i>the other direction!</i>

9
00:00:51,146 --> 00:00:56,050
{\an7}<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>Wait... he's not</i>
<i>one of those </i>
<i>white guys...</i>

10
00:00:56,083 --> 00:00:59,287
[sobbing]

11
00:00:59,320 --> 00:01:01,288
{\an1}Is he crying?

12
00:01:01,321 --> 00:01:04,723
{\an4}<i>(Shikamaru)</i>
<i>He looks like  </i>
a <i>kid! I can't </i>
<i>believe this war!</i>

13
00:01:04,757 --> 00:01:05,691
[roar]

14
00:01:10,328 --> 00:01:11,129
[gasp]

15
00:01:11,162 --> 00:01:14,697
[crying]

16
00:01:14,731 --> 00:01:19,368
{\an1}[struggling grunts]

17
00:01:20,436 --> 00:01:22,170
What's up with
this rain..!?

18
00:01:24,139 --> 00:01:26,675
[struggling]

19
00:01:32,312 --> 00:01:34,414
{\an1}<i>(Sukui)</i>
<i>We've got another</i>
<i>one, Sakura..!</i>

20
00:01:34,447 --> 00:01:35,615
Okay.

21
00:01:37,216 --> 00:01:38,849
{\an1}Put him over there,
on the table.

22
00:01:38,883 --> 00:01:39,850
{\an1}Okay, will do.

23
00:01:39,884 --> 00:01:41,285
{\an1}<i>(Sukui)</i>
<i>Let's grab</i>
<i>the next one!</i>

24
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:42,486
Right!

25
00:01:46,356 --> 00:01:47,457
[gasp]

26
00:01:48,325 --> 00:01:50,426
Who... are you?

27
00:01:50,459 --> 00:01:53,529
{\an1}[giggling]

28
00:01:53,562 --> 00:01:55,430
...What is this?

29
00:01:55,463 --> 00:01:57,532
{\an1}[giggling]
Huh?

30
00:02:04,670 --> 00:02:05,737
It's... snowing.

31
00:02:08,173 --> 00:02:10,675
[gasp] Hey! What
are you doing!?

32
00:02:11,476 --> 00:02:22,217
{\an4}(singing)
It's snowing kon!
It's snowing kon!
It's snowing kon!

33
00:02:22,251 --> 00:02:24,386
{\an1}What's... happening!?

34
00:02:24,852 --> 00:02:26,554
<i>(Sakura)</i>
<i>[scream]</i>

35
00:02:35,194 --> 00:02:36,195
[grunt]

36
00:02:39,464 --> 00:02:40,764
Beetle Sphere!

37
00:02:41,466 --> 00:02:42,400
Fang Over Fang!

38
00:02:42,433 --> 00:02:44,301
{\an1}Argh!

39
00:02:44,868 --> 00:02:45,868
Hm.

40
00:02:48,237 --> 00:02:49,238
[gasp]

41
00:02:51,307 --> 00:02:52,507
Akamaru!
[bark]

42
00:02:54,242 --> 00:02:56,343
Damn! Lightening
Style, huh?

43
00:02:56,377 --> 00:02:57,778
[barking]

44
00:02:57,811 --> 00:03:00,714
[gasp]

45
00:03:02,749 --> 00:03:04,450
[barking]

46
00:03:04,484 --> 00:03:06,518
Weird... do you
know who it is?

47
00:03:07,818 --> 00:03:11,489
{\an1}[angry grunts]

48
00:03:11,522 --> 00:03:12,856
He sounds angry.

49
00:03:12,889 --> 00:03:14,391
[barking]

50
00:03:16,925 --> 00:03:17,893
Whoa!

51
00:03:21,963 --> 00:03:24,766
{\an8}<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>Hold on, everyone...</i>
<i>I'm coming...</i>

52
00:05:11,482 --> 00:05:13,317
{\an1}What's with all
that rain..?

53
00:05:13,350 --> 00:05:16,786
{\an8}Do you think it's
a new enemy? This
is getting dull...

54
00:05:16,819 --> 00:05:19,589
{\an1}[struggling grunts]

55
00:05:19,988 --> 00:05:22,791
{\an1}[crying]

56
00:05:23,392 --> 00:05:25,459
{\an1}[struggling grunts]

57
00:05:26,327 --> 00:05:29,362
{\an1}[crying]

58
00:05:29,929 --> 00:05:32,866
{\an1}Expansion Jutsu!

59
00:05:32,898 --> 00:05:33,666
Huh?

60
00:05:33,867 --> 00:05:34,900
Choji!

61
00:05:34,933 --> 00:05:36,268
{\an1}Shikamaru!

62
00:05:36,968 --> 00:05:38,636
I'm sorry, Ino.

63
00:05:39,337 --> 00:05:41,606
Enough! Shadow
Strangle Jutsu!

64
00:05:44,007 --> 00:05:45,375
...complete.

65
00:05:45,908 --> 00:05:52,747
[crying louder]

66
00:05:52,781 --> 00:05:54,649
{\an1}[struggling grunts]

67
00:05:54,682 --> 00:05:57,384
How can he still
use jutsu while
he's captured!?

68
00:05:57,418 --> 00:05:59,386
This is bad!

69
00:06:01,053 --> 00:06:03,356
My sign's...
weakening!

70
00:06:03,389 --> 00:06:05,590
{\an1}This rain..!

71
00:06:06,991 --> 00:06:08,560
{\an1}[crying]

72
00:06:08,593 --> 00:06:09,927
I can't... move!

73
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:11,462
[grunt] Damn it!

74
00:06:11,961 --> 00:06:16,633
{\an1}Shikamaru! Choji!
Ino! It's me!

75
00:06:17,634 --> 00:06:20,869
{\an1}Hold on, how does
this kid know all
of our names!?

76
00:06:20,903 --> 00:06:23,337
Yeah, I've never
even seen him before.

77
00:06:23,371 --> 00:06:24,539
Neither have I.

78
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,008
[gasps]

79
00:06:30,444 --> 00:06:30,644
[grunt]

80
00:06:30,677 --> 00:06:30,976
{\an1}Ow!

81
00:06:31,010 --> 00:06:31,977
{\an3}Yarg!

82
00:06:32,445 --> 00:06:34,647
<i>(Yota)</i>
<i>It's snowing... kon!</i>

83
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:36,281
Huh? Ah!

84
00:06:38,917 --> 00:06:40,819
[grunt]

85
00:06:43,554 --> 00:06:46,923
[crying]

86
00:06:46,955 --> 00:06:48,458
{\an3}[gasp]

87
00:06:48,491 --> 00:06:49,692
{\an1}Huh?

88
00:06:49,725 --> 00:06:52,461
Huh? Wait...
I know you!

89
00:06:52,494 --> 00:06:53,829
It's you...

90
00:06:54,863 --> 00:06:56,096
Hey, you're...

91
00:06:56,130 --> 00:06:57,431
[barking]

92
00:06:58,666 --> 00:07:04,903
[giggles]

93
00:07:05,637 --> 00:07:06,705
Yota!

94
00:07:06,738 --> 00:07:07,673
{\an3}-Yota!
-Yota!

95
00:07:07,706 --> 00:07:08,639
{\an1}Yota!

96
00:07:09,407 --> 00:07:09,707
{\an3}Yota!

97
00:07:09,740 --> 00:07:10,775
{\an1}[bark]

98
00:07:11,441 --> 00:07:12,509
[giggle]

99
00:07:13,976 --> 00:07:17,546
{\an8}<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>Yota... that's right!</i>
<i>We do know you..!</i>

100
00:07:28,555 --> 00:07:30,924
{\an1}I think that they're
somewhere around here.

101
00:07:31,691 --> 00:07:35,660
{\an1}Those kunai are from
an important set!

102
00:07:36,094 --> 00:07:39,497
{\an5}Kunai are meant for
throwing, you know,
so you're bound to lose
them sooner or later.

103
00:07:39,530 --> 00:07:44,767
{\an4}I know, but this is
different! My mom bought
them for me as a reward for
getting into the Academy!

104
00:07:44,801 --> 00:07:46,336
[groan]

105
00:07:46,603 --> 00:07:49,404
If I lose them
my mom's gonna
be really upset!

106
00:07:51,072 --> 00:07:54,942
{\an5}Listen, okay?
Choji's a nice kid
so we're gonna help
him out, you got it?

107
00:07:54,976 --> 00:07:56,644
{\an1}Aw, what a drag.

108
00:07:58,845 --> 00:08:00,647
{\an1}Where are you, kunai?

109
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,748
{\an1}Damn it! Where
did you throw
them!?

110
00:08:02,781 --> 00:08:04,850
I don't see
them...

111
00:08:07,118 --> 00:08:07,919
Wha?

112
00:08:07,952 --> 00:08:08,887
Rain..?

113
00:08:09,487 --> 00:08:11,788
{\an1}Huh? That's weird.
It's sunny out!

114
00:08:11,822 --> 00:08:14,056
{\an1}What's with the
freaky weather?

115
00:08:15,525 --> 00:08:17,125
{\an1}<i>(Yota)</i>
<i>[crying]</i>

116
00:08:17,158 --> 00:08:18,360
Huh?

117
00:08:19,060 --> 00:08:21,530
{\an1}<i>(Yota)</i>
<i>[crying]</i>

118
00:08:21,563 --> 00:08:22,731
Huh?

119
00:08:22,764 --> 00:08:24,498
{\an1}Hey! Look!
What is that?

120
00:08:25,099 --> 00:08:25,900
What?

121
00:08:26,433 --> 00:08:27,902
{\an1}[crying]

122
00:08:27,935 --> 00:08:28,802
{\an3}[gasp]

123
00:08:28,836 --> 00:08:32,872
{\an1}[crying]

124
00:08:32,906 --> 00:08:35,641
Wait! That's
a little kid!

125
00:08:35,908 --> 00:08:39,443
Hey! My kunai!

126
00:08:39,477 --> 00:08:43,146
{\an1}[crying]

127
00:08:43,179 --> 00:08:45,615
What's wrong
with him?

128
00:08:45,649 --> 00:08:48,651
{\an1}Well he is kinda
stuck there because
of my kunai...

129
00:08:48,684 --> 00:08:50,118
But how did he
get up there?

130
00:08:50,151 --> 00:08:51,519
{\an1}Let's go help him!

131
00:08:51,553 --> 00:08:52,587
{\an1}Yeah!

132
00:08:53,521 --> 00:08:56,823
{\an1}[struggling grunts]

133
00:08:56,857 --> 00:08:58,792
{\an1}And get my
kunai, too!

134
00:08:58,825 --> 00:09:00,560
{\an1}[struggling grunts]

135
00:09:03,829 --> 00:09:06,063
{\an1}This is completely
pathetic...

136
00:09:06,096 --> 00:09:09,867
{\an4}Gimme a break! We
still haven't learned
the Tree Climbing
Jutsu yet--!

137
00:09:09,900 --> 00:09:13,871
{\an4}[grunt] So we can't
climb up to him as
easily as our dads
would have..!

138
00:09:13,904 --> 00:09:17,707
Yeah, but still..!
I gotta get my
kunai back!

139
00:09:17,740 --> 00:09:21,577
{\an1}[struggling grunts]

140
00:09:23,177 --> 00:09:27,881
[crying]

141
00:09:27,914 --> 00:09:28,481
[scream]

142
00:09:28,515 --> 00:09:30,149
{\an1}I can't climb
in this..!

143
00:09:31,017 --> 00:09:33,084
{\an1}[struggling grunts]

144
00:09:33,117 --> 00:09:35,486
Shikamaru!
Choji, wait!

145
00:09:35,854 --> 00:09:39,523
{\an1}[struggling grunts]

146
00:09:44,761 --> 00:09:48,430
No! No! Nooo!
Whoooaaaa!

147
00:09:53,634 --> 00:09:54,668
{\an1}Choji! No!

148
00:10:02,976 --> 00:10:06,210
{\an1}Hee! Fall down good!

149
00:10:06,243 --> 00:10:07,244
What..!?

150
00:10:07,278 --> 00:10:09,814
{\an1}[laughing]

151
00:10:09,847 --> 00:10:12,882
Hm?

152
00:10:12,916 --> 00:10:14,551
{\an1}[laughing]

153
00:10:14,584 --> 00:10:20,089
Huh... ha...
[laughing]

154
00:10:20,121 --> 00:10:21,956
Hm?
The rain...

155
00:10:22,190 --> 00:10:23,725
{\an1}...It stopped.

156
00:10:23,758 --> 00:10:28,695
[laughing]

157
00:10:28,729 --> 00:10:29,695
{\an1}Huh?

158
00:10:30,229 --> 00:10:34,499
[laughing]

159
00:10:34,532 --> 00:10:36,668
Hm? "Weather for sale?"

160
00:10:40,104 --> 00:10:43,573
<i>(Choji / Yota)</i>
<i>[laughing]</i>

161
00:10:47,843 --> 00:10:50,144
{\an3}Hm.

162
00:10:50,177 --> 00:10:50,879
{\an1}[gasp]

163
00:10:52,647 --> 00:10:53,648
[gasp]

164
00:11:00,619 --> 00:11:03,722
Your name is Yota
...isn't it?

165
00:11:03,756 --> 00:11:06,224
Yes, Yota! I
remember now!

166
00:11:06,257 --> 00:11:09,027
That's right! How
could we have all
forgotten?

167
00:11:22,569 --> 00:11:25,806
{\an1}Yota, you know you're
a reanimation, right?

168
00:11:25,839 --> 00:11:27,707
[gasp] He's
one, too..?

169
00:11:28,675 --> 00:11:35,312
{\an1}[crying]

170
00:11:35,346 --> 00:11:36,747
Huh?

171
00:11:36,781 --> 00:11:37,982
[screams]

172
00:11:38,683 --> 00:11:39,850
{\an1}[crying]

173
00:11:39,884 --> 00:11:41,217
[grunts]

174
00:11:41,251 --> 00:11:44,186
{\an1}That's right! Yota
can control the weather.

175
00:11:44,888 --> 00:11:49,223
{\an1}[crying]

176
00:11:49,257 --> 00:11:52,527
Yota! You have
to stop..!

177
00:11:53,293 --> 00:11:54,695
{\an3}Argh!

178
00:11:55,962 --> 00:11:59,732
{\an1}He's not doing it on
purpose! Yota's...
being controlled.

179
00:11:59,765 --> 00:12:01,333
{\an1}Then that means
Yota's already...

180
00:12:01,367 --> 00:12:05,937
[crying]

181
00:12:20,949 --> 00:12:23,150
{\an1}You call me...
Yota!

182
00:12:23,751 --> 00:12:25,786
{\an1}Yota..? That's
your name..?

183
00:12:25,820 --> 00:12:26,586
{\an1}Yeah!

184
00:12:26,619 --> 00:12:28,354
{\an1}Kind of a strange
name for a girl.

185
00:12:28,388 --> 00:12:29,756
{\an1}I a boy!

186
00:12:29,789 --> 00:12:31,724
A boy who sounds
like a girl?

187
00:12:31,757 --> 00:12:34,093
{\an1}That's right, you
got it! Just who
I am..!

188
00:12:34,126 --> 00:12:36,894
You're not actually
from the Hidden Leaf
Village, are you?

189
00:12:36,928 --> 00:12:38,295
{\an1}No, I am different.

190
00:12:38,328 --> 00:12:40,098
So where did
you come from?

191
00:12:40,131 --> 00:12:41,231
{\an1}Hm?

192
00:12:41,264 --> 00:12:43,066
{\an1}I from all over!

193
00:12:43,100 --> 00:12:45,901
{\an1}Whattaya mean, "all
over?" What nation?

194
00:12:45,935 --> 00:12:46,736
{\an1}<i>(Yota)</i>
<i>None!</i>

195
00:12:46,769 --> 00:12:47,136
Huh?

196
00:12:47,169 --> 00:12:48,269
{\an1}What village?

197
00:12:48,303 --> 00:12:49,038
{\an1}<i>(Yota)</i>
<i>None!</i>

198
00:12:49,071 --> 00:12:50,138
{\an3}Hmm...

199
00:12:50,171 --> 00:12:53,174
{\an1}[laughter]
Nope, none!
None... none!

200
00:12:53,208 --> 00:12:54,274
{\an1}<i>(Yota)</i>
<i>[giggles]</i>

201
00:12:56,110 --> 00:12:58,178
{\an1}I wonder if he's
lonely or something.

202
00:12:58,212 --> 00:13:00,213
{\an1}Yeah, it sure seems
like that's the case.

203
00:13:00,245 --> 00:13:04,683
{\an4}What should we do?
Should we go and tell
the grown-ups in the
Village about him?

204
00:13:04,716 --> 00:13:06,717
[sigh]

205
00:13:06,751 --> 00:13:07,885
But we can't!

206
00:13:07,918 --> 00:13:08,819
Why?

207
00:13:08,853 --> 00:13:10,888
Remember when that
stranger came to town?

208
00:13:10,921 --> 00:13:12,756
Everybody made a
big fuss about it!

209
00:13:12,789 --> 00:13:17,893
{\an5}A while ago, my dad
said there's been some
kind of big-big trouble
between the villages--

210
00:13:17,926 --> 00:13:19,761
So we can't!

211
00:13:19,794 --> 00:13:24,065
{\an4}Yeah. If someone like
Yota showed up in the
village, people would
ask a lot of questions.

212
00:13:24,098 --> 00:13:25,233
Hmmm...

213
00:13:25,899 --> 00:13:28,334
{\an1}Ha! Big-big!
[giggle]

214
00:13:28,667 --> 00:13:29,169
{\an3}Hm?

215
00:13:29,202 --> 00:13:32,004
{\an1}Ha! Big-big!
[giggle]

216
00:13:32,037 --> 00:13:34,039
{\an1}Hey, you are pretty
big-big, choji.

217
00:13:34,073 --> 00:13:35,206
[shocked gasp]

218
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,573
{\an1}Uhhh...

219
00:13:36,608 --> 00:13:39,743
I'm not really
big-big, I'm just what
you call a little chubby!

220
00:13:39,777 --> 00:13:41,277
{\an1}You're a
fatty-fatso!

221
00:13:41,310 --> 00:13:44,380
<i>(Choji)</i>
<i>Ugh! No! You're wrong!</i>

222
00:13:44,413 --> 00:13:45,380
[gasps]

223
00:13:45,413 --> 00:13:48,350
I am... NOT
A FATSO..!!

224
00:13:48,383 --> 00:13:49,851
Not good!!!

225
00:13:49,885 --> 00:13:52,053
Argh!

226
00:13:52,087 --> 00:13:54,255
{\an1}[giggling]

227
00:13:54,287 --> 00:13:59,192
Argh! Come here,
you...!

228
00:13:59,225 --> 00:14:02,394
[giggling]

229
00:14:02,427 --> 00:14:05,363
{\an1}Come here! I'm
gonna--! Huh?

230
00:14:05,396 --> 00:14:07,932
[fainting sigh]

231
00:14:07,965 --> 00:14:09,733
What's wrong, Yota?

232
00:14:09,766 --> 00:14:13,335
My poor tum-tum
is... empty-empty.

233
00:14:13,369 --> 00:14:14,370
{\an1}Tum-tum?

234
00:14:14,403 --> 00:14:17,206
[laughing]

235
00:14:23,077 --> 00:14:29,182
{\an1}[happily eating]

236
00:14:29,215 --> 00:14:32,118
Heh heh! Sure
looks like he's
enjoying himself.

237
00:14:32,151 --> 00:14:32,951
{\an1}Mhm!

238
00:14:32,984 --> 00:14:35,220
I'm kinda jealous.

239
00:14:35,253 --> 00:14:38,823
[happily eating]

240
00:14:38,856 --> 00:14:40,057
{\an1}More! More!

241
00:14:40,090 --> 00:14:41,457
We don't have
any more.

242
00:14:41,491 --> 00:14:43,159
You're asking a lot.

243
00:14:43,193 --> 00:14:46,762
{\an1}But I'm starving-
starving! And my
tum-tum's growling!

